    <title>Spatial Entanglement Sudden Death in Spin Chains at All Temperatures</title>
    <updated>2026-02-24T08:54:38Z</updated>
    <link href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.20694v1" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/>
